Package kea.exercise.hogwartsstudentadmin.edu.hogwarts.model

Class Teacher

java.lang.Object
kea.exercise.hogwartsstudentadmin.edu.hogwarts.model.Teacher
@Entity public class Teacher extends Object
The Teacher class is a model that represents a teacher in the Hogwarts Student Admin system. It contains information about the first name, middle name, last name, date of birth, house, head of house status, employment status, and employment dates of the teacher.
